==Irish==
===Pronunciation===
{{IPA|[ˈagəɲ]}}
===Prepositional pronoun===
[[First person]] [[plural]] [[pronoun]] fused with preposition [[ag]] '[[at]]'
#[[at]] [[us]]

===Usage===
Used as the predicate of the verb [[bí]] 'to [[be]]' to indicate possession:
:''Tá leabhar againn'' &mdash; We have a book

